<div type="apparatus">
<head>Apparatus</head>
<p>The letters read by us are highlighted.</p><p>ll.4, 10:ΜΕΝΙΠΠΙΟΥ Sherard, presumably misreading a ligature (certainly in 4)</p><p>l. 5, ΕΝΕΛΕΙ, Sherard, again misreading the ligature</p><p>l. 9, ΔΟΡΟΥ Sherard, ΔΩΡΟΥ Boeckh</p><p>l. 17, ΛΕΙΤΟΥΓΙΑΙΣ Sherard; ΛΕΤΟΥΓΙΑΙΣ, whence λε[ι]του[ρ]γίαις Boeckh</p><p>l. 19, Δ Sherard; Α, whence [δ´], Boeckh</p><p>l. 22, ΙΕΡΑ Sherard</p>

</div>
